    "-.05 0.05.1.15 2021m1 2021m7 2022m1 2022m7 2023m1 2023m7 2024m1 2024m7 (b) Occupation-Level Impacts (Pooled Diff-in-Diff) All Software Dev.",
    "Legal Prof. Accountants Customer Service Marketing Financial Advisors HR Prof. Office Clerks Teachers IT Support -.1 -.05 0.05.1.15 2023 2024 Notes: This figure shows changes in incumbent workers' outcomes by adoption rates, indexed to the launch of ChatGPT in November 2022, at the workplace-occupational level.",
